# galCIB

This package calculates 1-halo and 2-halo term angular power spectra, $C(\ell)$, and 3D power spectra, $P(k)$, for galaxies and CIB maps. 

It uses a halo-model approach to relating cosmic star formation rate, halo dust physics, and galaxy HOD to predict the power spectra. 
